name: Geni James
text: I've ordered pizza's from here by all methods;  phone, on-line and walk-in.  Every pizza, every time has been correct and fresh.  Only one small suggestion, I wish they would put just a little more cheese on the finished product.

name: Gretchen G.
text: The prices are right and the Chicken Mediterranean is amazing! And the service has always been good there even when there's a rush.

name: Lisa Thomasson
text: Great food and easy ordering.  On Tuesday all pizzas are only $10, and on Friday their large pepperoni, cheese or sausage pizzas are just $5 each!

name: Aaron
text: Good fresh pizza. Favorite is the gourmet veggie delite on thin crust

text: Always reliable and good quality. Better than other national chains and less expensive than boutique pizza shops.

text: You get your pizza custom made with whatever you choose and it's quite tasty! Great option for parties or family dinner. You take it home and bake it, so it's hot when you eat!
